1998-10-11  Federico Mena Quintero  <federico@nuclecu.unam.mx>

	* annotated-source.sgml: New file with a template for annotated
	source code.  It uses a callout list to point out areas of
	interest in the code.

	* chapter.sgml: New file with a template for a chapter.  Contains
	a good template for DocInfo (author group, title, copyright).
